This function enriches the variables dictionary

The python module must contain the following hook:

define_env(env):
    "Declare environment for jinja2 templates for markdown"

    env.variables['a'] = 5

    @env.macro
    def bar(x):
        ...

    @env.macro
    def baz(x):
        ...

    @env.filter
    def foobar(x):
        ...
